== About ==
This is a Generalized Linear Models (GLM) impelentation entirely in Fortran.


== Requirements ==
* A Fortran 2003 compiler
* Cmake (if not installing the R package)
* R (if installing the R package)


== Installation Instructions == 
For the R package, simply execute
R CMD INSTALL glm_0.1-0.tar.gz

For the library install, go to
glm/src/glm/
and enter 'make'.  A static and dynamic library will be placed in the
glm/src/glm/build
tree.
